No, we didn't work on Sundays, no, only on Saturdays.

00:30:36.320 --> 00:30:39.320
Well, there was no buses on Sundays then, you know.

00:30:39.320 --> 00:30:40.320
No.

00:30:40.320 --> 00:30:41.320
No Saturdays, yeah.

00:30:41.320 --> 00:30:46.320
Right. You know, as a job, would you have said that it was boring or?

00:30:46.320 --> 00:30:47.320
No.

00:30:47.320 --> 00:30:48.320
No?

00:30:48.320 --> 00:30:53.320
No, boring at all. I've got time to go, but it'd be boring.

00:30:53.320 --> 00:30:54.320
It was hard work then, isn't it?

