It was hard work, yes. It keeps you going then, especially if you've got to do your target, you've got to go quick.

00:31:02.320 --> 00:31:11.320
Right. And you didn't have any choice about leaving either factory, both, did the METO close, is that why you, the factory closed, is that why you were made redundant in?

