Well, when I started in Fishing Price, in the way, making those toys.

00:34:13.320 --> 00:34:19.320
That's what I can remember, making that little dog and things like that.

00:34:19.320 --> 00:34:23.320
And the women as well, you know, going out.

00:34:23.320 --> 00:34:31.320
And one time we were going in and they were taking us to...

00:34:31.320 --> 00:34:34.320
Oh, what's that name now?

00:34:34.320 --> 00:34:42.320
We had to go to another factory to do something there. I can't remember what it was, though.

00:34:42.320 --> 00:34:47.320
But we had to have the best to go. But we never did anything there.

00:34:47.320 --> 00:34:52.320
So, we enjoyed that. We were in the bus. I mean, friend in the bus we were.

00:34:52.320 --> 00:34:55.320
Not in Port Talbot.

00:34:55.320 --> 00:35:00.320
So, you were supposed to be showing another company, another group how to do things, were you?

00:35:00.320 --> 00:35:02.320
Or just meeting up with them?

00:35:02.320 --> 00:35:08.320
No, I think it's to show them how to do some toys there.

00:35:08.320 --> 00:35:12.320
I'm trying to picture where it was.

00:35:12.320 --> 00:35:19.320
But then we didn't get there. We didn't do anything in there.

00:35:19.320 --> 00:35:23.320
We were sitting outside. It was a lovely day. We just sat on the wall talking.

00:35:23.320 --> 00:35:26.320
We never went in the factory.

00:35:26.320 --> 00:35:31.320
I don't know what it was. We were doing something inside a factory or something, so we couldn't do nothing.

00:35:31.320 --> 00:35:37.320
So, we sat outside and we enjoyed buying ice cream. And that was some ice cream as well.

00:35:37.320 --> 00:35:41.320
I can't remember what it was.

00:35:41.320 --> 00:35:44.320
So, did they organise any trips out at all for you?

00:35:44.320 --> 00:35:46.320
Like a trip in the summer or something?

00:35:46.320 --> 00:35:47.320
No.

00:35:47.320 --> 00:35:50.320
Any parties for children or anything?

00:35:50.320 --> 00:35:56.320
No, nothing like that. Only that time we went out together for the Christmas.

00:35:56.320 --> 00:36:01.320
What about if you wanted to buy some of those toys? Could you do that? You know you had children.

00:36:01.320 --> 00:36:04.320
Oh yes, you can buy them.

