They were borrowing these, were they?

00:36:27.320 --> 00:36:29.320
Yeah, they were taking them.

00:36:29.320 --> 00:36:31.320
But was there a shop there that you could go and buy?

00:36:31.320 --> 00:36:34.320
Oh yes, there was a shop there. You could make them pricey, yeah.

00:36:34.320 --> 00:36:36.320
Were they cheaper then?

00:36:36.320 --> 00:36:43.320
Yeah, they were cheaper for us here. Because we were working there. You could buy them a lot of toys there if you wanted them, yeah.

00:36:43.320 --> 00:36:50.320
Were you a friend in Llyca? Did they ask you to buy some for them for Christmas and things? Were you allowed to do that?

